## Installation

```console
pip install wideprint
```

## Usage

`def print_columns(data:Iterable, columns:int=3, sep:str=" ", alignment:Literal[">","<","^"]=">")`
 
 ```python
 from wideprint import print_columns

 print_columns(
    data      = ["aaaa","b","c","d","e","f","g","h","i","j","kkk","l","m","n","o"],
    columns   = 3,
    sep       = "  ",
    alignment = "<"
)
 ```

 ```text
aaaa  b    c
d     e    f
g     h    i
j     kkk  l
m     n    o
```
